WEBVTT

01:42.560 --> 01:47.200
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL ZHU YU
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

01:53.560 --> 01:55.840
If the Emperor lacks virtue…

01:59.600 --> 02:01.920
let him abdicate, then.

02:12.480 --> 02:13.560
Yigui,

02:14.520 --> 02:15.520
mind your words.

02:19.840 --> 02:21.480
What was said today,

02:22.120 --> 02:23.040
neither I

02:23.800 --> 02:25.520
nor any of my ministers

02:26.800 --> 02:28.320
has heard a thing.

02:32.520 --> 02:33.520
Come. Let's drink

02:34.320 --> 02:35.320
and enjoy

02:36.440 --> 02:37.720
this moment together.

02:37.800 --> 02:39.160
UPHOLD VIRTUE, GRANT MERCY
CHERISH THE WORTHY, HONOR THE DIFFERENT

02:39.240 --> 02:40.600
Back then, only a handful of us

02:40.680 --> 02:42.760
heard that remark about abdication.

02:43.760 --> 02:46.880
Could someone have betrayed us?

02:51.320 --> 02:53.960
HEAR ALL SIDES

02:55.480 --> 02:56.920
I was not the fool.

02:57.520 --> 03:00.120
The late Emperor
was tyrannical and corrupt.

03:00.640 --> 03:02.160
The people suffered under his rule.

03:03.480 --> 03:05.280
And he feared the Crown Prince

03:05.360 --> 03:06.920
was too popular.

03:07.000 --> 03:10.800
So he deliberately elevated the Jia clan
and the Sixteenth Prince.

03:13.040 --> 03:14.560
If, back then,

03:14.640 --> 03:17.560
the Xie, Wei, and Qi families
had joined forces

03:18.080 --> 03:21.200
and placed Crown Prince Chengde
upon the throne,

03:22.240 --> 03:24.360
would the court have been clean
and the people at peace?

03:27.760 --> 03:29.440
But the Crown Prince

03:30.400 --> 03:32.040
was too indecisive.

03:32.600 --> 03:34.320
He lost the chance.

03:37.680 --> 03:41.000
The Crown Prince and Linshan
both died in battle.

03:41.080 --> 03:42.520
And you, Grand Tutor,

03:43.040 --> 03:45.080
spent your days in gloom,
cast aside and ignored.

03:45.160 --> 03:48.400
Tell me, would I really betray myself?

03:50.120 --> 03:52.000
The Crown Prince once said

03:52.080 --> 03:55.240
that Li Xing, though born
of an upright scholarly line,

03:55.320 --> 03:57.000
was obsessed with power.

03:57.080 --> 03:58.880
-Could it be…
-Exactly.

03:58.960 --> 04:00.720
The moment Crown Prince
set out for Jinzhou,

04:00.800 --> 04:03.480
his fate was sealed.
It was a dead end from the start.

04:04.080 --> 04:06.120
The Crown Prince is foolish,

04:06.840 --> 04:08.840
led astray by flatterers.

04:09.800 --> 04:13.680
He even dared dream of taking my throne.

04:15.120 --> 04:18.000
What say you, my ministers?

04:18.079 --> 04:20.000
Your Majesty is wise
and will judge rightly.

04:20.079 --> 04:20.720
PRINCE CHANGXIN SUI TUO

04:20.800 --> 04:22.280
I serve in the far northwest

04:22.360 --> 04:23.960
and know little of the court's affairs.

04:24.760 --> 04:26.080
I dare not speak rashly.

04:33.920 --> 04:36.280
For the sake of the realm,

04:37.760 --> 04:38.680
I

04:39.640 --> 04:41.760
must do what pains me most.

04:42.600 --> 04:46.000
Nephew, will you lend your strength?

04:47.040 --> 04:51.160
You are the son of my imperial sister,

04:52.440 --> 04:56.520
with half the blood
of the imperial family in you.

04:58.320 --> 05:00.000
Your Majesty means…

05:07.120 --> 05:12.200
I would share the realm with you

05:13.560 --> 05:15.760
and bind our houses in lasting alliance.

05:23.720 --> 05:28.440
The late emperor gave Prince Changxin
a hollow promise

05:28.960 --> 05:31.600
and made him refuse to send troops.

05:32.800 --> 05:34.440
To rid himself of his own son,

05:34.520 --> 05:36.880
he even invited wolves into the house.

05:37.600 --> 05:39.680
Truly a ruler without virtue.

05:41.400 --> 05:42.640
The late emperor

05:42.720 --> 05:45.560
forged letters in Rongyin's hand
to summon me back to the capital…

05:45.640 --> 05:46.480
QINGYUAN PALACE

05:46.560 --> 05:49.400
…while I was on my way
to send reinforcements.

05:52.560 --> 05:53.440
Yan,

05:53.520 --> 05:55.240
while the fire spreads,
you must leave now.

05:55.320 --> 05:57.760
No. We leave together.

05:59.880 --> 06:01.080
Lord Wei, you…

06:01.160 --> 06:02.880
If I had not cut my losses and escaped,

06:03.520 --> 06:05.800
I would have been branded a traitor
who defiled the palace.

06:06.640 --> 06:07.920
The Wei clan

06:08.000 --> 06:10.600
would have been exterminated
to the ninth generation.

06:10.680 --> 06:11.840
Get out!

06:13.000 --> 06:13.960
Yan,

06:14.720 --> 06:16.000
you go first.

06:20.680 --> 06:21.680
Rongyin!

06:23.480 --> 06:26.440
Do not worry. I will handle things here.

06:35.760 --> 06:39.840
The Xie, Qi, and Wei families
served Dayin for three generations.

06:40.440 --> 06:42.800
We fought until our flesh
and blood were spent.

06:43.320 --> 06:45.160
Yet that dog of an emperor

06:45.680 --> 06:47.880
toyed with us like pieces on a board!

06:54.960 --> 06:56.600
As for what came after,

06:57.520 --> 06:59.760
Grand Tutor, you know it well enough.

07:00.960 --> 07:03.720
It was I who bathed the palace in blood.

07:03.800 --> 07:05.720
Had I not launched a coup,

07:06.240 --> 07:08.080
tell me, how could I have survived?

07:13.720 --> 07:15.760
After Rongyin died,

07:16.440 --> 07:18.880
I seized that dog emperor by the throat

07:18.960 --> 07:21.440
and forced him to write
the edict of abdication.

07:24.080 --> 07:26.160
Only by taking control of the court myself

07:27.040 --> 07:29.480
could Dayin remain stable

07:31.320 --> 07:34.640
and the realm endure.

07:40.680 --> 07:42.160
The disgrace laid upon Wei Qilin

07:42.240 --> 07:44.280
was also something
I had no choice but to do.

07:44.360 --> 07:46.680
The late emperor's scheme

07:47.200 --> 07:49.560
was far too thorough.

07:49.640 --> 07:51.920
Before returning to the capital,

07:52.000 --> 07:54.720
I entrusted the tiger tally
to the man I trusted most, Wei Qilin,

07:54.800 --> 07:56.640
and ordered him
to seek reinforcements in my place.

07:56.720 --> 07:58.960
Your Highness, the tiger tally is genuine.

07:59.040 --> 08:01.000
Please send the troops at once.

08:01.600 --> 08:03.240
This tally is fake.

08:03.320 --> 08:04.160
It does not match.

08:05.680 --> 08:08.440
Everything had already been arranged
by the late Emperor.

08:13.680 --> 08:16.000
Later, misled by Qi Min,

08:16.080 --> 08:19.040
Zheng reopened the Jinzhou case
from 17 years ago

08:19.560 --> 08:21.440
and discovered that Wei Qilin's family
was still alive.

08:22.560 --> 08:23.920
Silencing them

08:24.440 --> 08:27.120
was the only way to preserve the bond
between uncle and nephew.

08:27.200 --> 08:29.320
Who would have thought
that fate would intervene.

08:29.920 --> 08:32.360
Zheng was saved by Fan Changyu.

08:33.720 --> 08:35.880
Heaven's will cannot be escaped.

08:43.240 --> 08:44.600
Truly…

08:46.920 --> 08:52.440
when emperors play their games,
loyal ministers die unjustly.

08:56.240 --> 08:57.480
So, in the end,

08:59.200 --> 09:01.920
I have still lost.

09:13.880 --> 09:15.160
Shall we go in?

09:27.480 --> 09:28.360
Let's leave.

09:34.960 --> 09:36.240
Fortunately,

09:36.320 --> 09:39.560
Xie Zheng, who is the blade himself,
finally found its sheath.

09:40.600 --> 09:41.600
Fan Changyu.

09:43.360 --> 09:45.640
Let me borrow Changyu's words.

09:46.480 --> 09:49.040
In this life, be a good pig.

09:49.640 --> 09:50.880
In the next life,

09:51.920 --> 09:53.960
be a good man.

10:01.160 --> 10:03.080
A man like me…

10:05.560 --> 10:08.000
will surely fall into the depths of hell.

10:12.400 --> 10:14.640
There will be no next life
for someone like me.

10:25.240 --> 10:27.280
Little wooden horse,

10:28.120 --> 10:30.840
clip-clopping along.

10:30.920 --> 10:37.520
A young boy, brave and proud.

10:38.880 --> 10:44.520
Sword in hand, singing battle songs,

10:45.760 --> 10:52.240
driving all the enemies away.

11:06.720 --> 11:08.160
Time for morning court.

11:08.680 --> 11:09.520
Morning court.

11:09.600 --> 11:11.080
Morning court.

11:13.960 --> 11:15.280
My ministers,

11:15.360 --> 11:17.360
who has a matter to present before me?

11:17.440 --> 11:20.000
Chancellor Wei, why are you kneeling?

11:20.520 --> 11:22.520
Am I really that frightening?

11:23.960 --> 11:25.200
Never mind.

11:25.280 --> 11:27.040
If there's nothing further,
court is dismissed.

11:27.640 --> 11:29.440
In the end, this realm

11:30.480 --> 11:32.000
can only depend on me.

11:33.080 --> 11:36.000
Depend on me. Depend on me.

11:37.320 --> 11:38.240
Brother.

11:41.080 --> 11:43.280
Look what I brought you.

11:45.360 --> 11:46.400
All your favorite things.

11:47.160 --> 11:48.520
Candied plums

11:49.600 --> 11:50.760
and your beloved osmanthus pastries.

11:51.360 --> 11:52.960
Come. Have a bite.

11:57.360 --> 11:59.400
Delicious. Delicious!

12:02.000 --> 12:04.160
Slow down. You will choke.

12:07.000 --> 12:08.040
Delicious.

12:08.920 --> 12:09.800
Brother.

12:11.480 --> 12:13.040
Do you still recognize

12:14.000 --> 12:15.360
who I am?

12:39.320 --> 12:40.680
Wha… What?

12:43.280 --> 12:44.200
Brother.

12:44.280 --> 12:45.360
What did you say?

12:46.920 --> 12:48.640
I am wise. Yes.

12:50.400 --> 12:51.520
What did you say?

13:15.000 --> 13:17.520
I thought you would not come.

13:21.200 --> 13:22.800
Someone had to see you off.

13:24.160 --> 13:25.600
You may break your promises.

13:27.280 --> 13:28.360
I do not.

13:29.320 --> 13:30.400
I must say,

13:31.680 --> 13:33.800
you even made soup for me.

13:34.960 --> 13:35.920
Very kind of you.

13:37.280 --> 13:38.920
Even a condemned prisoner

13:39.680 --> 13:41.200
is given a last meal

13:41.280 --> 13:43.320
before execution, doesn't he?

13:44.720 --> 13:46.000
Feed me.

13:47.160 --> 13:48.960
Do not waste your effort.

14:21.520 --> 14:22.520
What is it?

14:23.760 --> 14:24.760
You pity me?

14:43.240 --> 14:44.640
The flavor is good,

14:46.280 --> 14:47.360
though it has gone cold.

14:55.760 --> 14:56.880
Do you know

14:57.720 --> 15:00.880
when I truly fell for you?

15:02.880 --> 15:03.880
I do.

15:05.000 --> 15:06.400
But if I could do it again…

15:08.520 --> 15:10.080
I'd never have pulled you
out of that water.

15:11.800 --> 15:15.320
You were the only one who saw my face

15:15.960 --> 15:17.160
and did not recoil in fear.

15:18.280 --> 15:19.600
Your reward.

15:41.600 --> 15:43.040
And in you,

15:43.920 --> 15:46.280
I saw something I had long yearned for.

15:48.680 --> 15:49.680
Freedom.

15:55.120 --> 15:56.800
You once had that too.

15:58.000 --> 15:59.320
It was right in front of you.

16:01.360 --> 16:03.320
But you hid it behind your mask.

16:10.600 --> 16:13.720
Thank you for keeping your word.

16:16.560 --> 16:18.080
You hate me so much…

16:20.120 --> 16:22.040
yet you still gave me what I asked for.

16:25.360 --> 16:26.280
Yu Qianqian.

16:27.480 --> 16:29.440
I truly liked you.

16:32.000 --> 16:33.000
That is why,

16:34.240 --> 16:35.800
if there is another life,

16:37.120 --> 16:38.160
I hope

16:39.880 --> 16:41.440
we never meet again.

16:45.800 --> 16:46.840
Is there more?

16:47.960 --> 16:49.240
Do not let it go to waste.

17:20.200 --> 17:21.640
At the very end…

17:23.760 --> 17:25.680
You once told me

17:26.440 --> 17:27.599
that if you died,

17:27.680 --> 17:28.880
you could return home.

17:31.360 --> 17:32.840
I want to know

17:34.840 --> 17:36.600
who you truly are.

17:40.480 --> 17:41.920
A wandering ghost?

17:43.680 --> 17:45.400
A fallen immortal?

17:46.640 --> 17:47.960
Tell me.

17:50.280 --> 17:52.320
Let me die knowing the truth.

17:56.880 --> 17:58.160
I am just myself.

17:59.720 --> 18:01.040
I am Yu Qianqian.

18:06.200 --> 18:07.120
You…

18:08.680 --> 18:10.840
You liar.

18:53.520 --> 18:54.360
Are you alright?

19:04.960 --> 19:05.800
Changyu,

19:06.400 --> 19:07.720
I have a secret.

19:10.160 --> 19:12.720
I came from a place very, very far away.

19:13.920 --> 19:15.400
I might never be able to return.

19:18.120 --> 19:19.360
If it is that far away,

19:20.160 --> 19:21.520
then do not go back.

19:22.160 --> 19:24.240
Come back to Lin'an.
We will live there in peace.

19:33.960 --> 19:34.800
Come on.

19:55.600 --> 19:59.080
DAYIN

19:59.160 --> 20:00.680
In the 18th year of Yongping,

20:01.200 --> 20:04.960
Yu Bao'er's name was formally registered
in the imperial genealogy.

20:05.480 --> 20:08.800
His mother, Empress Dowager Yu,
renamed him Qi Yu.

20:09.760 --> 20:15.040
That spring, the new emperor ascended
the throne and began the Yongxing era.

20:15.760 --> 20:19.600
His birth mother, Lady Yu,
was honored as Empress Dowager Mingde

20:19.680 --> 20:22.080
and granted authority
to rule from behind the curtain.

20:22.680 --> 20:24.800
The late Huaihua Commandant Wei Qilin

20:24.880 --> 20:27.440
was posthumously granted the title
Count Zhongyong.

20:27.520 --> 20:31.240
The late General Meng Shuyuan
was posthumously named Marquis Wusu.

20:32.000 --> 20:35.440
Marquis Wu'an, Xie Zheng,
was appointed Prince Regent

20:35.520 --> 20:37.280
to oversee affairs of state.

20:37.360 --> 20:40.440
Fan Changyu was elevated
to General Huaihua

20:41.040 --> 20:43.840
and granted the rank
First Rank Lady Protector of the Realm.

20:43.920 --> 20:45.400
Together, they help govern the court.

20:46.520 --> 20:48.360
The new emperor took the throne
at a young age.

20:49.000 --> 20:50.600
With the Three Excellencies sharing power,

20:51.120 --> 20:52.640
both court and people looked forward

20:53.160 --> 20:54.640
to peace across the land.

20:58.320 --> 20:59.720
Long live the Emperor!

21:04.480 --> 21:06.200
Long live the Emperor!

21:11.720 --> 21:13.520
Long live the Emperor forever!

21:19.360 --> 21:25.280
Long live the Emperor!
Long live the Emperor forever!

21:26.840 --> 21:30.240
GUARD YOUR THOUGHTS

21:32.440 --> 21:34.240
Do not forget what you promised me.

21:34.840 --> 21:35.880
Your mother is not here.

21:35.960 --> 21:37.400
Hurry and eat some more.

21:40.320 --> 21:41.640
Do not worry, Changning.

21:41.720 --> 21:43.160
When I hold power one day,

21:43.240 --> 21:45.800
I will not go against the Prince Regent
or General Huaihua.

21:45.880 --> 21:47.880
Only weak emperors grow suspicious
of loyal ministers.

21:48.480 --> 21:50.080
When you finally take power,

21:50.160 --> 21:52.040
could you make me a princess too?

21:55.000 --> 21:56.200
You want to be a princess?

21:57.200 --> 21:58.200
Like the physician lady.

21:58.280 --> 21:59.680
She looks so impressive.

21:59.760 --> 22:01.080
When I get married,

22:01.160 --> 22:03.800
my husband must offer his family's
entire fortune as a bride price.

22:03.880 --> 22:06.320
The whole realm belongs to me.

22:06.400 --> 22:08.600
No one has more wealth than I do.

22:09.280 --> 22:10.760
Would you like to be my empress?

22:10.840 --> 22:13.520
You are giving me
the imperial palace as my bride price?

22:13.600 --> 22:16.160
Not just the palace. The entire realm.

22:16.240 --> 22:17.680
The entire realm?

22:18.320 --> 22:19.680
What does that mean?

22:19.760 --> 22:20.920
It means…

22:21.600 --> 22:23.520
from the battlefield,
where your sister fights,

22:23.600 --> 22:24.440
to this palace,

22:24.520 --> 22:26.760
and even farther south,

22:26.840 --> 22:28.000
all of it belongs to me.

22:28.080 --> 22:29.800
If you become my empress,

22:29.880 --> 22:31.320
then it will all belong to you.

22:31.920 --> 22:33.160
That big?

22:33.240 --> 22:35.680
Even my falcon would need
days of flying to reach it.

22:37.000 --> 22:38.440
You cannot go back on your word.

22:38.520 --> 22:40.000
Let's make a promise.

22:42.160 --> 22:43.720
-Pinky swear.
-Pinky swear.

22:43.800 --> 22:45.160
-A hundred years, never to change.
-A hundred years, never to change.

22:45.240 --> 22:47.320
-Only puppies break the promise.
-Only puppies break the promise.

22:48.240 --> 22:51.320
Qi Yu, how many times today
have you had sweets sent in?

22:51.400 --> 22:52.720
You will ruin your teeth!

22:53.360 --> 22:54.600
Come here!

22:55.960 --> 22:57.240
Come here right now!

23:01.280 --> 23:03.200
You are getting more disobedient
by the day.

23:03.280 --> 23:04.560
-Pretty Lady, do not hit him!
-Mother!

23:04.640 --> 23:05.720
Changning, be good.

23:05.800 --> 23:07.200
-Do you know how many cavities
-Pretty lady…

23:07.280 --> 23:08.320
-you already have?
-Please!

23:08.400 --> 23:09.760
-And you still run?
-Pretty lady…

23:10.280 --> 23:11.520
Come here!

23:12.840 --> 23:14.360
Do not run.

23:23.360 --> 23:24.320
Get over here.

23:24.400 --> 23:25.880
You skip your writing practice…

23:25.960 --> 23:26.800
HUMBLE YOURSELF AND STAY ON GUARD

23:26.880 --> 23:28.560
…yet you still sneak sweets. Come here.

23:28.640 --> 23:31.960
LI RESIDENCE

23:34.840 --> 23:36.120
Careful with that.

23:36.720 --> 23:37.680
Oh no, that…

23:54.320 --> 23:55.760
The estate's confiscated. Watch yourself.

23:57.640 --> 23:58.760
Stand over there.

24:15.360 --> 24:16.280
Grandfather,

24:17.160 --> 24:18.360
wars with Northern Jue

24:18.880 --> 24:20.840
have drained Dayin's treasury.

24:22.280 --> 24:24.200
Our family has donated everything we own.

24:24.840 --> 24:26.480
Let it serve as atonement for our crimes.

24:27.080 --> 24:29.240
His Majesty and the Prince Regent
keep their word.

24:29.760 --> 24:31.160
They will not pursue past offenses.

24:32.320 --> 24:33.760
Please set your mind at ease

24:34.440 --> 24:35.680
and retire to a peaceful life.

24:39.280 --> 24:42.480
Peaceful retirement?

24:44.360 --> 24:45.960
Call it what it is.

24:46.600 --> 24:48.760
Confiscation and exile.

24:51.760 --> 24:54.240
The crimes of our family
were unforgivable.

24:55.040 --> 24:56.800
This is already the best outcome.

24:58.200 --> 25:00.040
If they had shown no mercy,

25:01.720 --> 25:03.040
the entire Li clan

25:04.120 --> 25:05.800
would have been wiped out.

25:13.040 --> 25:16.040
I played the villain for nothing.

25:18.320 --> 25:21.120
Seventeen years ago,

25:22.280 --> 25:25.600
I became the villain for nothing.

25:49.520 --> 25:50.680
Wenkan,

25:51.200 --> 25:52.480
have you truly

25:52.560 --> 25:54.160
asked to be exiled to the frontier,

25:55.040 --> 25:57.640
to suffer in that frozen wasteland?

26:07.880 --> 26:08.840
Perhaps

26:10.600 --> 26:12.680
this is the best ending
fate could have arranged.

26:37.240 --> 26:39.440
LIN'AN

26:39.520 --> 26:43.720
Changyu is back!

26:44.480 --> 26:46.000
-Changyu!
-Changyu!

26:49.800 --> 26:51.880
Changyu is back!

26:51.960 --> 26:53.840
-Changyu!
-You are back!

26:54.360 --> 26:56.200
Changyu is back!

26:56.280 --> 26:58.200
NOODLE SOUP

26:58.280 --> 27:00.080
Changyu, you are back!

27:01.160 --> 27:02.800
Mrs. Fan!

27:02.880 --> 27:03.840
Changyu!

27:04.840 --> 27:05.880
Changyu!

27:05.960 --> 27:07.440
Mrs. Fan!

27:07.520 --> 27:11.200
Greetings, General Huaihua.

27:11.280 --> 27:13.960
-Please.
-General Huaihua!

27:14.040 --> 27:16.160
-Changyu!
-Changyu is back!

27:16.240 --> 27:17.800
You are back!

27:18.480 --> 27:19.320
LUO'S PAWNSHOP

27:19.400 --> 27:20.800
Mrs. Fan is back!

27:21.400 --> 27:23.240
Mrs. Fan is back!

27:24.200 --> 27:26.520
SUN’S BAMBOO WORKS

27:26.600 --> 27:27.440
Changyu!

27:28.760 --> 27:29.880
You are back!

27:32.080 --> 27:34.320
-General Huaihua!
-Mrs. Fan!

27:36.040 --> 27:37.320
Changyu!

27:37.400 --> 27:38.920
Changyu!

27:39.000 --> 27:39.960
Changyu!

27:40.040 --> 27:41.160
Changyu!

27:44.000 --> 27:45.000
You are back!

27:49.040 --> 27:50.600
Changyu is back!

28:21.080 --> 28:23.920
You have waited long
for this moment, haven't you?

28:43.160 --> 28:44.920
SPIRIT TABLET OF MENG LIHUA
SPIRIT TABLET OF WEI QILIN

28:45.000 --> 28:46.040
All I ask

28:46.120 --> 28:49.360
is that they come home soon.

28:52.120 --> 28:54.320
Milady, that is enough.

28:54.840 --> 28:56.880
They are blessed with good fortune.

28:56.960 --> 28:58.360
They will be fine.

28:58.440 --> 29:00.200
You men would never understand.

29:01.040 --> 29:04.800
You do not know how a mother feels
when a piece of her heart is torn away.

29:05.400 --> 29:06.920
Do we look that important?

29:07.920 --> 29:10.920
You think we could just go around
being the parents of General Huaihua?

29:11.000 --> 29:12.600
What nonsense are you thinking?

29:15.040 --> 29:16.160
Mr. Zhao! Mrs. Zhao!

29:18.920 --> 29:19.960
Zhao.

29:20.040 --> 29:21.480
Zhao, listen!

29:22.080 --> 29:23.440
We are back!

29:23.960 --> 29:24.800
Is that Ning's voice?

29:24.880 --> 29:28.160
-Miss them so much, you're hearing things?
-Mr. Zhao! Mrs. Zhao!

29:28.240 --> 29:29.920
-Listen.
-Listen to what?

29:30.440 --> 29:31.560
Mr. Zhao! Mrs. Zhao!

29:35.000 --> 29:36.000
It is true.

29:36.080 --> 29:37.560
They really came back.

29:38.200 --> 29:39.120
Is anyone…

29:40.880 --> 29:42.280
Mr. Zhao! Mrs. Zhao!

29:43.800 --> 29:45.000
Changyu.

29:45.760 --> 29:46.800
Changyu!

29:48.000 --> 29:49.280
You are really back!

29:49.360 --> 29:50.320
Mr. Zhao.

29:50.880 --> 29:51.920
Mrs. Zhao.

29:52.000 --> 29:52.840
You are tanned.

29:52.920 --> 29:55.600
And thinner too. You poor child.

29:55.680 --> 29:56.720
It is good you are back.

29:59.160 --> 30:00.000
Mother.

30:00.520 --> 30:01.800
Father.

30:02.320 --> 30:03.960
I came back safe and sound.

30:04.920 --> 30:06.800
I will serve you both as your daughter.

30:06.880 --> 30:08.200
We will never be separated again.

30:08.280 --> 30:10.040
I will take care of you too.

30:11.360 --> 30:14.120
Changyu. What did you just call us?

30:14.200 --> 30:15.800
On her way home,

30:15.880 --> 30:18.000
she kept thinking of changing
how she addresses you.

30:18.600 --> 30:20.000
She hopes you will allow it.

30:21.800 --> 30:26.000
-Good.
-How could we deserve such a blessing?

30:26.600 --> 30:28.720
As long as you are staying,
that is all that matters.

30:29.480 --> 30:31.400
No matter how grand the officials
or how wide

30:31.480 --> 30:32.520
the world outside,

30:32.600 --> 30:33.840
nothing compares to home.

30:33.920 --> 30:36.000
Nothing compares to having
your parents beside you.

30:37.560 --> 30:39.160
No more parting, children.

30:39.240 --> 30:41.360
We will never be separated again.

30:42.160 --> 30:43.640
Mr. Zhao! Mrs. Zhao!

30:43.720 --> 30:44.960
We are back!

30:47.160 --> 30:49.840
Mr. Zhao, Mrs. Zhao,
we all made it back safe.

30:50.360 --> 30:52.120
We will take care of you together.

30:58.560 --> 30:59.760
Jin Yuanbao.

30:59.840 --> 31:01.560
You have grown up.

31:02.120 --> 31:03.480
Come, come, get up.

31:05.040 --> 31:06.240
Man Cang.

31:06.320 --> 31:08.240
You are still as sturdy as ever.

31:10.240 --> 31:11.840
-Man Wu.
-Mrs. Zhao.

31:13.800 --> 31:14.920
Where is Man Di?

31:15.720 --> 31:17.840
One is still missing.

31:20.040 --> 31:21.160
Mother.

31:23.640 --> 31:24.800
Man Di

31:25.320 --> 31:27.040
did not make it back.

31:35.920 --> 31:38.320
How could one be missing?

31:40.280 --> 31:41.240
Good children.

31:41.760 --> 31:43.000
You are home now.

31:43.080 --> 31:44.120
You are home now.

31:44.200 --> 31:45.480
You are home.

31:46.000 --> 31:47.520
Come. Come inside.

31:47.600 --> 31:49.920
-Quick, come inside.
-Come in!

31:50.000 --> 31:52.280
Come. You are home now, Changning.

31:52.360 --> 31:53.320
We are home!

32:00.840 --> 32:03.880
SPIRIT TABLET OF ZISU, A DEAR FRIEND

32:03.960 --> 32:07.640
SPIRIT TABLET OF FULING, A DEAR FRIEND

32:07.720 --> 32:10.720
SPIRIT TABLET OF LAN SHUHUI, A DEAR FRIEND

32:21.600 --> 32:24.160
SALVATION FOR ALL

32:25.800 --> 32:26.640
Mother!

32:27.440 --> 32:28.880
-Mother!
-Your Majesty,

32:28.960 --> 32:30.840
you should address her as Mother Empress.

32:32.200 --> 32:33.600
Mother Empress, come here.

32:39.520 --> 32:40.760
What is it?

32:41.560 --> 32:43.600
Mother Empress, I want to issue a decree.

32:43.680 --> 32:46.160
I want to make Changning my empress.

32:47.240 --> 32:49.720
Then you should ask
whether Changning is willing first.

32:50.440 --> 32:53.120
Last time Changning asked me
to make her a princess.

32:53.200 --> 32:54.400
I did not want to,

32:54.480 --> 32:55.640
so I made her empress instead.

32:56.520 --> 32:58.120
Changning already agreed.

32:58.200 --> 32:59.680
We even pinky swore.

33:01.640 --> 33:02.640
That still will not do.

33:03.480 --> 33:04.440
Why not?

33:05.240 --> 33:07.120
Because you are both still children.

33:07.200 --> 33:08.840
You cannot marry yet.

33:09.440 --> 33:10.840
Wait until you turn 20.

33:10.920 --> 33:12.200
Then you can ask Changning again.

33:12.280 --> 33:13.120
All right.

33:15.080 --> 33:16.240
It is snowing!

33:38.120 --> 33:39.400
At the third quarter of noon…

33:42.240 --> 33:44.000
Wei Yan will be executed now.

33:59.520 --> 34:00.360
Yigui,

34:01.200 --> 34:04.320
this wine was prepared by Jiuheng himself.

34:05.280 --> 34:06.520
It will spare you…

34:09.400 --> 34:11.280
from the torture
of death by a thousand cuts.

34:37.920 --> 34:39.840
Another year of falling snow.

34:41.639 --> 34:45.600
Another year of falling snow.

34:50.639 --> 34:52.880
Did you anger your uncle again?

34:52.960 --> 34:55.000
Uncle is so strict when he teaches.

34:55.080 --> 34:56.040
And he has no patience.

34:56.120 --> 34:57.320
He is always scolding me.

34:58.920 --> 35:00.000
Uncle!

35:00.080 --> 35:00.920
I won!

35:10.320 --> 35:11.800
So you finally came.

35:45.280 --> 35:46.360
It is getting late.

35:48.880 --> 35:49.920
You should head home.

36:16.880 --> 36:17.720
Wei Yan, once Grand Chancellor.

36:17.800 --> 36:18.640
Though he rendered great service
as regent, his crimes cannot be excused.

36:18.720 --> 36:19.560
First, the Jinzhou disaster
claimed 100,000 soldiers.

36:19.640 --> 36:20.480
Then the frontier burned
with relentless war.

36:20.560 --> 36:21.200
Treason, betrayal, deceit, kinslaying,
and the ruin of order.

36:21.280 --> 36:21.840
Making mortals the fuel for his flame,

36:21.920 --> 36:22.560
though raising
the banner of peace for all,

36:22.640 --> 36:23.520
is still a crime beyond forgiveness.

36:23.600 --> 36:24.400
Sentenced to death. Property confiscated.

36:24.480 --> 36:25.360
Let posterity judge his life.

36:25.440 --> 36:28.040
In this life, be a good pig.

36:28.560 --> 36:29.760
In the next life,

36:30.760 --> 36:32.720
be a good man.

36:34.160 --> 36:36.320
A man like me…

36:38.520 --> 36:41.240
will surely fall into the depths of hell.

36:43.520 --> 36:45.360
There will be no next life
for someone like me.

37:05.920 --> 37:07.960
TWO MONTHS LATER

37:08.040 --> 37:11.440
XIGU ALLEY

37:13.360 --> 37:14.560
Excuse me. Let me pass.

37:15.960 --> 37:17.120
Did you know?

37:17.200 --> 37:18.960
Ever since we came back to Xigu Alley,

37:19.040 --> 37:21.440
this tree somehow became
a matchmaking tree.

37:21.960 --> 37:24.800
People say the fate between
General Huaihua and the Prince Regent

37:24.880 --> 37:26.400
began right here under this tree.

37:26.480 --> 37:27.920
How did the story turn into that?

37:28.440 --> 37:30.960
You dragged me home
from the snowy ferry crossing.

37:31.040 --> 37:33.360
Anyway, people say
this tree is very powerful.

37:33.440 --> 37:35.760
If you toss a red ribbon into the branches

37:35.840 --> 37:37.320
and two ribbons tangle together,

37:37.400 --> 37:40.080
then that person is your destined one.

37:40.160 --> 37:41.480
You really believe that?

37:41.560 --> 37:42.520
It is true.

37:42.600 --> 37:43.960
A lot of people made wishes here

37:44.040 --> 37:46.160
and later met the one meant for them.

37:58.280 --> 38:00.920
Did we really have to sneak out
in the middle of the night

38:01.000 --> 38:02.960
like thieves just to come here?

38:04.200 --> 38:07.040
If people saw the two of us
coming here to pray in person,

38:07.560 --> 38:09.080
they would laugh us to death.

38:18.160 --> 38:19.040
You go.

38:20.640 --> 38:21.680
Afraid?

38:22.200 --> 38:23.240
I'm the head of the house.

38:23.760 --> 38:24.920
My ribbon should be catching yours.

38:26.840 --> 38:27.680
All right.

38:32.240 --> 38:33.080
Let's do it.

38:36.640 --> 38:38.360
It has to catch.

38:45.200 --> 38:46.560
-That doesn't count.
-What are you doing?

38:46.640 --> 38:47.640
I am trying again.

38:48.280 --> 38:50.200
I need to pull it down and throw it again.

38:50.280 --> 38:51.280
Ours are not tangling.

38:51.360 --> 38:53.600
It is fine. They already tangled.

38:53.680 --> 38:54.560
Where?

38:54.640 --> 38:57.120
-I can't even tell whose ribbon that is.
-Trust me.

38:57.800 --> 38:58.720
In this life,

38:59.240 --> 39:00.400
the next life,

39:00.480 --> 39:01.560
and every life after,

39:02.600 --> 39:03.600
we are tied together.

39:08.640 --> 39:09.800
Still, I want to take it down.

39:09.880 --> 39:10.960
Come on. Let's go.

39:11.040 --> 39:13.600
-Put me down!
-No.

39:13.680 --> 39:14.640
Did you hear me?

39:14.720 --> 39:15.560
I did not.

39:16.200 --> 39:17.440
I have to get back!

40:08.200 --> 40:15.160
CHANGYU AND ZHENG,
TOGETHER FOREVER AND EVER

40:19.360 --> 40:20.640
XIE

40:20.720 --> 40:25.680
FIVE YEARS LATER, JINZHOU MILITARY CAMP

40:26.680 --> 40:28.280
I haven't been
to a military camp in years.

40:28.800 --> 40:30.400
The memories come flooding back.

40:31.080 --> 40:31.920
They do.

40:32.520 --> 40:33.480
Form ranks!

40:36.760 --> 40:37.840
-Form ranks!
-Form ranks!

40:37.920 --> 40:38.760
Move it!

40:38.840 --> 40:40.080
Prince Regent. General Huaihua.

40:40.160 --> 40:41.320
Northern Jue forces invaded.

40:41.400 --> 40:42.800
Blood-clad Cavalry is assembling.

40:43.560 --> 40:45.680
Changyu, I'll have someone
escort you back to Lin'an.

40:45.760 --> 40:47.560
What are you talking about?
I am going with you.

40:47.640 --> 40:48.480
Do not be absurd.

40:49.000 --> 40:50.080
When did you last see battle?

40:50.160 --> 40:51.640
Do not underestimate me.

40:51.720 --> 40:52.880
I did not earn the title

40:52.960 --> 40:54.600
of General Huaihua by sitting around.

40:54.680 --> 40:56.480
-Someone!
-Yes!

40:56.560 --> 40:58.080
-Bring me my armor.
-Yes!

41:18.480 --> 41:19.400
General Xie,

41:19.480 --> 41:21.920
if things turn dangerous, hide behind me.

41:22.920 --> 41:25.200
You are a mother of two.
Time to stop making jokes.

41:26.480 --> 41:27.960
Then be careful.

41:28.680 --> 41:29.520
Come back safe.

41:30.040 --> 41:30.880
Come back safe.

41:46.720 --> 41:50.080
THE END

41:50.720 --> 41:53.120
END CREDIT SCENE

41:55.080 --> 41:59.880
IF THE JINZHOU TRAGEDY
17 YEARS AGO HAD NEVER HAPPENED

42:06.680 --> 42:09.080
Zheng is really devoted
to practicing his sword.

42:11.080 --> 42:12.320
A few days ago,

42:12.840 --> 42:14.240
his father pointed out

42:14.320 --> 42:15.920
that his sword forms
were not solid enough.

42:16.440 --> 42:17.480
So lately,

42:17.560 --> 42:19.520
aside from eating, sleeping, and studying,

42:19.600 --> 42:20.640
he spends all his spare time

42:20.720 --> 42:22.120
right here practicing.

42:24.480 --> 42:25.760
Ever since he was little,

42:25.840 --> 42:27.720
he has been stubborn like this.

42:28.360 --> 42:30.320
He does not resemble me at all.

42:30.840 --> 42:32.000
Nor his father.

42:32.720 --> 42:33.960
He takes after his uncle.

42:36.040 --> 42:37.560
They say nephews are like their uncles.

42:37.640 --> 42:39.200
That saying exists for a reason.

42:42.640 --> 42:44.080
The little one in my belly though

42:44.160 --> 42:45.920
is quite lazy.

42:46.440 --> 42:47.880
Already full term

42:47.960 --> 42:49.600
and she barely moves.

42:50.120 --> 42:51.400
I am thinking

42:52.120 --> 42:54.720
she will be a quiet girl.

42:56.960 --> 42:58.400
But whenever her father teases her,

42:58.480 --> 43:00.240
she suddenly kicks so hard,

43:00.320 --> 43:03.040
she nearly scares him to death.
He spent the whole night awake

43:03.120 --> 43:05.000
worrying to me,

43:05.520 --> 43:06.840
"What if it turns out to be a boy?"

43:08.920 --> 43:09.840
What is wrong with that?

43:09.920 --> 43:12.480
General Wei likes daughters that much?

43:13.640 --> 43:15.360
He was positively smug about it.

43:15.880 --> 43:18.480
He told me, "If it is a girl,
we will name her Changyu."

43:19.080 --> 43:20.200
And if it is a boy?

43:20.280 --> 43:21.960
He said boys are tough.

43:22.480 --> 43:24.800
We would just call him Rocky

43:24.880 --> 43:26.160
or Buster for now.

43:26.760 --> 43:27.600
When he grows older,

43:27.680 --> 43:29.240
his grandfather can give him
a proper name.

43:34.560 --> 43:35.600
I have heard

43:36.120 --> 43:38.000
there is an old folk trick.

43:38.920 --> 43:42.000
Let a child guess whether the baby
in a pregnant woman's belly

43:42.520 --> 43:44.360
is a boy or a girl.

43:44.440 --> 43:45.920
-Shall we try it?
-Why not?

43:46.000 --> 43:47.200
Zheng.

43:48.320 --> 43:50.040
Come here to me.

43:52.600 --> 43:53.600
Let me ask you something.

43:54.680 --> 43:56.800
What do you think
is inside Aunt Meng's belly?

43:56.880 --> 43:59.680
A little boy or a little girl?

44:03.440 --> 44:04.480
A little girl.

44:06.600 --> 44:08.200
If it is a little girl,

44:08.280 --> 44:09.320
then you must marry her

44:09.920 --> 44:11.480
and bring her home as my daughter-in-law.

44:12.600 --> 44:14.520
Why would she become your daughter-in-law?

44:17.840 --> 44:20.160
Because I like her.

44:25.840 --> 44:26.680
All right.

44:47.680 --> 44:50.680
"If it is a girl,
we will name her Changyu."

45:02.840 --> 45:06.080
CHANGYU

45:06.160 --> 45:08.400
WHERE CLOUDS MEET VERDURE

45:10.680 --> 45:11.560
Greetings, Madam.

45:12.400 --> 45:13.240
Thanks for coming.

45:13.320 --> 45:14.720
How is she? Has she delivered?

45:14.800 --> 45:17.000
Yes. Mother and daughter are both safe.

45:17.080 --> 45:19.160
I was sent to deliver the good news.

45:19.240 --> 45:20.120
Thank you, Nanny.

45:20.200 --> 45:21.520
Please come inside.

45:23.680 --> 45:25.000
It was kind of her to send word.

45:25.680 --> 45:28.000
I've prepared a small gift
to show my regards.

45:29.560 --> 45:30.400
Thank you.

45:30.920 --> 45:32.480
How is she doing?

45:33.480 --> 45:34.760
She is doing well.

45:35.280 --> 45:36.880
Please help pass along a message.

45:36.960 --> 45:38.680
In a few days, I will come visit her.

45:38.760 --> 45:39.880
Very well.

45:39.960 --> 45:41.520
Madam, please stay.

45:41.600 --> 45:42.680
Thank you for your trouble.

45:57.560 --> 45:59.800
Mother, did Aunt Meng give birth?

46:00.400 --> 46:01.240
She did.

46:02.240 --> 46:03.160
What is it?

46:03.840 --> 46:06.600
Zheng, are you already
thinking about your little bride?

46:22.920 --> 46:24.360
CHANGYU'S BIRTHDAY, FIFTH YEAR OF QINGHE

46:24.440 --> 46:25.640
17TH DAY, 1ST MONTH

46:25.720 --> 46:30.120
CHANGYU'S BIRTHDAY
17TH DAY, 1ST MONTH, 5TH YEAR OF QINGHE

46:33.040 --> 46:35.480
SIXTEEN YEARS LATER

46:35.560 --> 46:36.800
Over the past five years,

46:36.880 --> 46:38.480
Father has worn down
the Northern Jue forces

46:38.560 --> 46:39.960
until their treasury is nearly empty.

46:41.040 --> 46:42.680
And now those old men at court

46:42.760 --> 46:44.240
are calling for a ceasefire.

46:44.320 --> 46:46.200
Is that not the same
as handing the Northern Jue army

46:46.280 --> 46:48.760
a chance to recover
and strike again later?

46:50.440 --> 46:52.040
I came to the capital in Father's place

46:52.560 --> 46:54.080
to persuade His Majesty

46:54.680 --> 46:57.160
to continue
and march for their stronghold.

46:57.240 --> 46:58.400
We could wipe them out.

46:59.640 --> 47:00.920
Do you really think

47:01.520 --> 47:04.320
those old ministers are the ones
calling for the ceasefire?

47:07.080 --> 47:08.800
Your father's campaigns these past years

47:08.880 --> 47:10.640
have been steady and measured.

47:11.440 --> 47:12.680
His aim has always been

47:12.760 --> 47:14.680
to grind down Northern Jue's strength

47:14.760 --> 47:16.960
until they collapse entirely.

47:18.160 --> 47:21.280
But His Majesty does not see it that way.

47:22.520 --> 47:24.000
But my father has always been

47:24.080 --> 47:25.440
absolutely loyal to His Majesty.

47:26.680 --> 47:28.040
Twenty years ago, His Majesty

47:28.120 --> 47:32.080
was much like
the present Crown Prince Qi Min.

47:32.160 --> 47:33.440
Virtuous and upright.

47:34.920 --> 47:36.640
Yet over the years, his attitude

47:36.720 --> 47:38.680
toward the Eastern Palace has changed.

47:39.320 --> 47:43.080
He fears history repeating itself.

47:43.600 --> 47:45.560
He guards against it,

47:45.640 --> 47:47.200
even with his own son.

47:48.000 --> 47:50.600
So imagine how he must regard
a lord stationed in the northwest,

47:50.680 --> 47:54.160
commanding a hundred thousand troops,
and not even of the imperial clan.

47:54.240 --> 47:56.920
How could he possibly
leave such a man unchecked?

48:00.480 --> 48:01.320
Enough.

48:01.880 --> 48:04.840
Set aside the matter
of attacking Northern Jue for now.

48:05.400 --> 48:07.040
If you bring this up again

48:07.120 --> 48:08.320
before His Majesty,

48:08.400 --> 48:10.280
His Majesty will still find excuses

48:10.360 --> 48:13.840
to brush it aside,
talking about floods in the south

48:13.920 --> 48:15.200
and other affairs of state.

48:19.560 --> 48:20.840
Thank you for the advice.

48:21.360 --> 48:22.520
No need for that.

48:22.600 --> 48:23.600
Oh, by the way,

48:23.680 --> 48:25.920
your aunt prepared some dishes.

48:26.000 --> 48:27.080
Let's go eat.

48:28.680 --> 48:29.680
You are finally

48:29.760 --> 48:32.360
old enough to share a few drinks with me.

48:33.480 --> 48:36.680
These days, even Father
and General Wei cannot outdrink me.

48:37.200 --> 48:39.680
Tonight I will see whether you can
hold your wine better than I can.

48:40.840 --> 48:42.840
So the fledgling has grown his wings.

48:43.640 --> 48:47.920
Very well.
Let's settle it at the wine table.

48:48.000 --> 48:48.840
Please.

48:48.920 --> 48:50.400
BY IMPERIAL GRACE

48:52.240 --> 48:52.920
YIXIANG RESTAURANT

48:53.000 --> 48:54.640
Guests, please come inside.

48:54.720 --> 48:55.560
Very well.

48:56.160 --> 48:57.280
This way, please.

48:59.560 --> 49:00.560
Please.

49:09.760 --> 49:11.560
-Careful.
-Strange.

49:11.640 --> 49:13.560
Lin'an felt oddly familiar.

49:20.240 --> 49:22.360
You two must also be guests
from the capital.

49:23.080 --> 49:23.920
Please come upstairs.

49:24.000 --> 49:25.680
The other guests are waiting for you.

49:27.400 --> 49:28.360
Ms. Yu,

49:29.320 --> 49:30.960
you look familiar.

49:31.480 --> 49:33.160
Have we met somewhere before?

49:35.040 --> 49:36.600
Funny you should say that.

49:36.680 --> 49:38.240
Now that you mention it,

49:38.320 --> 49:39.760
I feel the same.

49:40.640 --> 49:42.960
Perhaps in a past life,
we were good friends.

49:43.880 --> 49:45.880
Come. Let me treat you to our specialties.

49:47.760 --> 49:48.600
Let's go.

49:50.600 --> 49:52.360
You must all be tired from the journey.

49:52.440 --> 49:53.400
Allow me to offer a toast.

49:53.920 --> 49:54.880
-Come.
-Come, come.

49:55.400 --> 49:56.400
To your hard work.

49:56.480 --> 49:57.520
Bottoms up.

50:06.640 --> 50:07.840
Thank you all for waiting.

50:16.720 --> 50:19.080
This is our restaurant's signature dish,
snow frog soup.

50:19.160 --> 50:20.600
Honored guests, please enjoy.

50:21.280 --> 50:23.600
-Smells decent enough.
-Snow frog soup?

50:24.360 --> 50:25.200
It smells wonderful.

50:38.960 --> 50:40.960
Sir, would you like to try some?

50:55.480 --> 50:57.480
Sir, are you feeling unwell?

51:05.200 --> 51:06.360
I will go change.

51:07.000 --> 51:07.880
Please enjoy yourselves.

51:22.240 --> 51:24.520
Sir, are you truly all right?

51:26.720 --> 51:27.600
It is nothing.

51:27.680 --> 51:29.400
Please go about your work, Ms. Yu.

51:32.840 --> 51:34.560
The soup tastes great, and you throw up.

51:35.080 --> 51:36.880
I am this pretty, and you still throw up.

51:37.640 --> 51:39.080
What on earth is wrong with you?

51:44.880 --> 51:46.000
Are you all right?

51:50.160 --> 51:51.760
Your Highness values talent and courtesy.

51:52.400 --> 51:55.760
Why such an aversion
to a mere innkeeper today?

51:56.360 --> 51:57.720
I tried the soup just now.

51:57.800 --> 51:59.320
There was nothing unusual about it.

52:01.600 --> 52:03.120
I do not know why either.

52:04.640 --> 52:06.720
Perhaps she was an enemy of mine
in a past life.

52:08.240 --> 52:09.360
When I see her,

52:09.880 --> 52:11.400
my heart is strangely pleased,

52:11.920 --> 52:13.240
yet I cannot go near.

52:14.200 --> 52:15.400
The moment I do, I feel sick.

52:18.520 --> 52:20.520
That's why they say
fate brings people together,

52:21.880 --> 52:23.280
but destiny keeps them apart.

54:51.200 --> 54:54.840
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
IN THE MAKING OF THIS EPISODE

54:54.920 --> 54:55.800
Subtitle translation by: Jiaxin Wang
